  "text": "ROC-optimized cut-off values as well as sensitivities and specificities were calculated. [CITATION_1] Data analysis was performed using IBM SPSS Statistics for Windows, version 19.0 (IBM Corp., Armonk, NY, USA) and MedCalc version 18.2.1 (MedCalc Software bvba, Ostend, Belgium). All tests were twotailed, and a p-value of <0.05 was considered statistically significant.",
